title: 'Westworld' cast tease new series at premiere
text:
'Westworld' cast tease new series at premiere Tuesday, April 17, 2018 - 01:48 
Actress Evan Rachel Wood believes she is the biggest theorist of the show's non-linear narrative and 'still figuring out' what is going on. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
